ic that, until now, improvements in carbon efficiency\nper unit of production worldwide has been dramatically insufficient.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Jan 2011 15:13:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Mar 2011 09:46:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 17 Mar 2011 20:27:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-17"}
